---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Founding Team Meeting — Feb 2026 | Asmakam" description="Summary of the first founding team meeting held on February 28, 2026 in Indore.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Page Hero -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-forest via-forest/90 to-leaf"></div>
      <div class="container-wide mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
        <p class="font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-green-300 mb-3 animate-fade-in-up">Founding Team Meeting</p>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white font-bold mb-4 animate-fade-in-up drop-shadow-lg">
          First Founders' Huddle
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-green-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-up">
          Saturday, February 28, 2026 &middot; Indore
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 animate-fade-in-up">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/15 text-green-100 text-sm font-body">Harish</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/15 text-green-100 text-sm font-body">Archana</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/15 text-green-100 text-sm font-body">Maitreyi</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/15 text-green-100 text-sm font-body">Arpit</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/15 text-green-100 text-sm font-body">Manish</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-cream">
      <div class="container-narrow mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="section-title mb-6">Overview</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            The first founding team meeting of Asmakam brought together all five founders in Indore to discuss
            the future direction, audience, and identity of Asmakam Life University. The conversation spanned
            infrastructure planning, audience definition, individual motivations, financial sustainability, and
            the philosophical underpinnings of the project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Discussion Points -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-narrow mx-auto">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-10 text-center">Key Discussion Points</h2>
        <div class="space-y-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">

          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-sand to-cream">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">Defining Success & Future Plans</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-text-muted">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span>The team explored what success looks like in the next 12 months and 5 years.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Manish</strong> proposed infrastructure completion in the next year, with clarity on three horizontals: Pan Indore, Pan India, and International. He stressed having an outline for courses.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Arpit</strong> agreed on infrastructure completion — buildings, roads, and plantation.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Archana</strong> is most concerned with defining the target audience.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Maitreyi</strong> suggested identifying an age range, considering location tiers, and narrowing scope.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-sand to-cream">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">Identifying the Audience — "Who are we serving?"</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-text-muted">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Archana</strong> described two intentions: serving selflessly <em>and</em> serving a group that will support sustaining the space.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Arpit</strong> thinks the selfless aspect aligns better with core values. They should clarify "who" for outsiders to understand.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Harish</strong> shared two philosophical concepts: fixing vs. serving, and working on oneself instead of changing the world. Finding what gives joy will define the audience.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Arpit's</strong> focus: children and soil. <strong>Archana's</strong> focus: health, natural healing, waste materials.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-sand to-cream">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">Personal Motivations & "The Who"</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-text-muted">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Manish</strong> clarified that the target audience should come from individual motivations — what gives joy and what each person wants to work on.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Manish</strong> also shared a personal goal of creating a dense forest.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Maitreyi</strong> wants to build a community focused on mental health to address increasing isolation in her generation.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span>Concern raised: with five different interests, a common understanding of "who" and the vision must be created to avoid being "all over the place".</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-sand to-cream">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">Reclaiming Agency & Defining Scope</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-text-muted">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Archana</strong> introduced "zero outsourcing" (food, health, education) and "reclaiming your agency over your own life" as brand-defining statements.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Maitreyi</strong> argued these statements are hard to digest and too philosophical. <strong>Arpit</strong> called them "scary".</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span>Team shifted to defining a community: youth, families, people wanting to work on health. <strong>Maitreyi</strong> introduced wellness as a revenue-generating vertical.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span><strong>Archana</strong> suggested the outside audience (Pan-India/globally) may be easier to target.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-sand to-cream">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">The Matrix: Sustainability, Life Skills & Wellness</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 font-body text-text-muted">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span>Three verticals emerged as a matrix: <strong>Health</strong>, <strong>Work</strong>, and <strong>Nature</strong>.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span>Team acknowledged they can't execute on 15 things — need to pick and focus tactically and strategically for success in 12 months.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span>Concerns about logistical viability at the space. Agreement to not rush — focus on what's possible now and content creation.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-leaf mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span><span>Decision: keep things "mutely explicit" — start testing the waters with small programs before committing fully.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Takeaways -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-sand">
      <div class="container-narrow mx-auto">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-10 text-center">Key Takeaways</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-forest font-heading font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Infrastructure First</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted text-sm">Complete infrastructure development (buildings, roads, planting) within the next 12 months.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-forest font-heading font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Three Audience Tiers</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted text-sm">Focus on Pan Indore, Pan India, and International audiences — each needing different approaches.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-forest font-heading font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Young Parents as Core Audience</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted text-sm">Team agrees young parents are a primary target demographic, along with individuals seeking lifestyle disease reversal through body awareness and self-healing.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-forest font-heading font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Financial Sustainability</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted text-sm">Create a plan that balances for-profit ventures (revenue) with non-profit service. Financial viability is essential to sustain the vision.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-forest font-heading font-bold">5</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Three Verticals</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted text-sm"><strong>Health</strong>, <strong>Work</strong>, and <strong>Nature</strong> emerged as the core verticals forming the Asmakam matrix.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-forest font-heading font-bold">6</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Start Small, Test & Learn</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted text-sm">Don't rush. Keep things "mutely explicit" — test the waters with small programs before committing. Allow for emergence.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Action Items -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-narrow mx-auto">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-10 text-center">Action Items</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-saffron/5 border border-saffron/20">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-saffron/40 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-medium text-text-primary">Define a one-line brand statement for Asmakam</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">All five founders should align on a clear, simple sentence that anyone can understand. Avoid overly philosophical framing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-saffron/5 border border-saffron/20">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-saffron/40 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-medium text-text-primary">Each founder: write down personal "who" and "what"</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Individual exercise — who do you want to serve and what brings you the most joy? Find the overlaps.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-saffron/5 border border-saffron/20">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-saffron/40 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-medium text-text-primary">Draft 2-3 pilot programs across Health, Work, Nature</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Small, testable programs to validate demand and refine the offering. Start testing the waters.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-saffron/5 border border-saffron/20">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-saffron/40 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-medium text-text-primary">Create a 12-month infrastructure roadmap</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Buildings, roads, plantation — what's the timeline and milestones? Assign ownership.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-saffron/5 border border-saffron/20">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-saffron/40 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-medium text-text-primary">Build a financial sustainability plan</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Separate for-profit and non-profit streams. Define what generates revenue and what is offered selflessly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-saffron/5 border border-saffron/20">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-saffron/40 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-body font-medium text-text-primary">Start content creation</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-1">Begin building an audience through content even before the physical space is ready. Focus on what can be done now.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Notable Quotes -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-sand">
      <div class="container-narrow mx-auto">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-10 text-center">Notable Quotes</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-forest pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-heading text-lg italic text-text-primary leading-relaxed">"We are not here to fix anybody... We are here to serve because we are already whole."</p>
            <cite class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-2 block not-italic">— Harish</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-leaf pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-heading text-lg italic text-text-primary leading-relaxed">"We are trying to work on zero outsourcing for food, health and education — reclaiming your agency over your own life."</p>
            <cite class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-2 block not-italic">— Archana</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-earth pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-heading text-lg italic text-text-primary leading-relaxed">"Asmakam is where holistic development is a possibility."</p>
            <cite class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-2 block not-italic">— Manish</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-saffron pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-heading text-lg italic text-text-primary leading-relaxed">"Selfless wala angle can go into our core values maybe... More than defining who we are serving."</p>
            <cite class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted mt-2 block not-italic">— Arpit</cite>
          </blockquote>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Open Questions -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-cream">
      <div class="container-narrow mx-auto">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-10 text-center">Open Questions</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-forest/10">
            <span class="text-gold text-xl shrink-0">?</span>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted">How to balance revenue generation with selfless service? What's for-profit and what's non-profit?</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-forest/10">
            <span class="text-gold text-xl shrink-0">?</span>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted">How will marketing efforts resonate with the target audience and effectively communicate Asmakam's value proposition?</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-forest/10">
            <span class="text-gold text-xl shrink-0">?</span>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted">What specific steps can narrow the focus and avoid being "all over the place" across five different passions?</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-white border border-forest/10">
            <span class="text-gold text-xl shrink-0">?</span>
            <p class="font-body text-text-muted">What does the "mutely explicit" approach look like in practice? What are the first small experiments?</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer note -->
    <section class="py-8 bg-forest/5">
      <div class="container-narrow mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted">
          This summary was auto-generated from the audio recording of the founding team meeting using AI transcription.
          <br/>It is intended for internal team reference only.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
